Anthropic lawsuit proceedings: First legal assessments of the constitutionality of the supply chain risk decree are expected.

112
00:14:40,287 --> 00:14:51,237
Whether other tech companies will file as amicus curiae — as seen recently with Google and OpenAI employees acting in solidarity — is one of the interesting side questions.

113
00:14:51,237 --> 00:15:08,762
GPT-5.4 in practice: First real-world user experiences with the 1M context and computer use will reveal whether the OSWorld benchmark numbers hold in productive workflows — or whether the known latency and cost challenges at maximum context limit adoption.

114
