Firefox 148 patch notes: Mozilla will document the vulnerabilities found by Claude in the release notes.

115
00:15:16,262 --> 00:15:25,462
How many of the 14 high-severity bugs were exploitable in the wild will retrospectively assess the true urgency of the Mozilla-Anthropic project.

116
00:15:25,462 --> 00:15:41,362
Copilot Cowork feedback: First reports from the Frontier Program will show whether Microsoft Wave 3 with Claude under the hood represents a genuine workflow revolution — or whether the integration still stumbles on the known M365 inertia problems.

